definitionCn: 平滑肌肉瘤是源于肠壁平滑肌、肠壁血管平滑肌或肠壁黏膜肌的恶性间叶组织肿瘤,占所有软组织肿瘤的5%～10%。以直肠平滑肌肉瘤最多见,约占大肠平滑肌肉瘤的85%。常见发病部位为腹膜后区,可有疼痛。发生于下腔静脉的平滑肌肉瘤因部位不同而症状各异。平滑肌肉瘤除局部浸润邻近器官和组织外,血行播散是最主要的转移途径。
definitionEn: sarcoma containing large spindle cells of smooth muscle; although it rarely occurs in soft tissue, it is common in the viscera; the most common soft tissue sarcoma of the uterus and retroperitoneal region.
Pathogeny: The causes of leiomyosarcoma are unknown.
DifferentialDiagnosis: There is a wide differential diagNOSis, which includes spindle cell carcinoma, spindle cell melanoma, fibrosarcoma, malignant peripheral nerve sheath tumor and even biphenotypic sinonasal sarcoma.

name: UndifferentiatedPleomorphicSarcoma/MalignantFibrousHistiocytoma
未分化多形性肉瘤/恶性纤维组织细胞瘤

CTImageDescription:
generally heterogeneous
commonly demonstrate central low attenuation representing necrosis 12
calcification exceedingly rare
MRIImageDescription:
May frequently demonstrate cystic foci within. Signal characteristics include T1: isointense to muscle 
T2 non-fat suppressed: intermediate to hypointense to neighbouring fat 
T2 FS: predominantly hyperintense
DifferentialDiagnosisInCN: 平滑肌肉瘤的影像诊断无特征性,病理诊断主要根据肿瘤光镜下的形态特点,结合免疫组化来确诊。如果肿瘤不具备本类型肿瘤的形态特征,不应只根据免疫组化结果来作出诊断。
